@HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### Fetch the OpenAPI document (most variants)
GET {{HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### GET / - Hello world (FIRST, DOCUMENTtransformer1, DOCUMENTtransformer2,
###   DOCUMENTtransformerUse999, DOCUMENTtransformerInOut, SWAGGERUI,
###   MAPOPENAPIWITHAUTH, MAPOPENAPIWITHCACHING, OPENAPIWITHSCALAR,
###   OPERATIONtransformer1)
GET {{HostAddress}}/

### GET / - Returns JSON body with decimal amount (SCHEMAtransformer1)
GET {{HostAddress}}/
Accept: application/json

### GET /weatherforecast (DEFAULT)
GET {{HostAddress}}/weatherforecast
Accept: application/json

### GET /old - Deprecated endpoint (OPERATIONtransformer2)
GET {{HostAddress}}/old

### GET /new - Replacement endpoint (OPERATIONtransformer2)
GET {{HostAddress}}/new

### Fetch "internal" OpenAPI document (MULTIDOC_OPERATIONtransformer1)
GET {{HostAddress}}/openapi/internal.json
Accept: application/json

### Fetch "public" OpenAPI document (MULTIDOC_OPERATIONtransformer1)
GET {{HostAddress}}/openapi/public.json
Accept: application/json

### GET /world - Internal endpoint (MULTIDOC_OPERATIONtransformer1)
GET {{HostAddress}}/world